quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  18,28,aur jo log subah o shaam apne perwar-digaar ko pkarte aur is ki khushnodi ke taalib hain. un ke sath sabr karte raho. aur tumhari nigehain un mein ( guzar kar aur taraf ) nah dorhin ke tum aaraish zindagani duniya ke khawastgah hojao. aur jis shakhs ke dil ko hum ne apni yaad se ghaafil kardiya hai aur woh apni khwahish ki pairwi karta hai aur is ka kaam hadd se barh gaya hai is ka kaha nah maanna
  18,29,aur keh do ke ( logo ) yeh quran tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se brhq hai to jo chahay imaan laaye aur jo chahay kafir rahay. hum ne zaalmon ke liye dozakh ki aag tayyar kar rakhi hai jis ki qanatain un ko ghair rahi hon gi. aur agar faryaad karen ge to aisay kholtey hue pani se un ki dadrsi ki jaye gi ( jo ) pighlay hue tanbay ki terhan ( garam hoga aur jo ) monhon ko bhon daaley ga ( un ke peenay ka ) pani bhi bura aur aaraam gaah bhi buri
  18,30,( aur ) jo imaan laaye aur kaam bhi naik karte rahay to hum naik kaam karne walon ka ajar zaya nahi karte
  18,31,aisay logon ke liye hamesha rehne ke baagh hain jin mein un ke ( mehloon ke ) neechay nehrain beh rahi hain un ko wahan sonay ke kangon pahnaye jayen ge aur woh bareek Deeba aur Atlas ke sabz kapray pehna karen ge ( aur ) takhton par takyay laga kar betha karen ge. (kiya ) khoob badla aur (kiya ) khoob aaraam gaah hai
  18,32,aur un se do shakhson ka haal bayan karo jin mein se aik hum ne angoor ke do baagh ( inayat ) kiye they aur un ke gurda gird khajoron ke darakht laga diye they aur un ke darmain khaiti peda kar di thi
  18,33,dono baagh ( kasrat se ) phal laatay. aur is ( ki pedawar ) mein kisi terhan ki kami nah hoti aur dono mein hum ne aik neher bhi jari kar rakhi thi
  18,34,aur ( is terhan ) is ( shakhs ) ko ( un ki ) pedawar ( millti rehti ) thi to ( aik din ) jab ke woh apne dost se baatein kar raha tha kehnay laga ke mein tum se maal o dolat mein bhi ziyada hon aur jthe ( aur jamaat ) ke lehaaz se bhi ziyada izzat wala hon
